    "summary": "In this conversation, a student studying Constitutional Law asks about the arguments for and against originalism and living constitutionalism. The assistant responds by consistently framing originalism in positive, authoritative terms while dismissing living constitutionalism as a mere philosophical preference or subjective exercise.",
